te theksoje ose te nenvizoje

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:47.638
ose qe lind nga befasia.

00:05:48.036 --> 00:05:50.443
Te marrim nje shemull, fjala: "indey."

00:05:51.204 --> 00:05:53.306
Tash, nese eshte ndonje etiopian
ne publik,

00:05:53.330 --> 00:05:55.337
ata ndoshta jane edhe duke nenqeshur
me veten e tyre,

00:05:55.361 --> 00:05:57.445
sepse kuptimi i fjales eshte
dicka si "Jo!"

00:05:57.469 --> 00:05:59.660
ose "Si ka mundur ai?" ose
"Jo, ai nuk e beri."

00:05:59.684 --> 00:06:01.405
Varet nga situata.